title: Contributions to percent change in GDPNow: Real Personal Consumption Expenditures: Goods
notes: The Contributions to percent change in GDPNow: Real Personal Consumption Expenditures: Goods represents the contribution in percentage points that the nowcast for Personal Consumption Expenditures: Goods provides to real GDP growth.
